%% ============================================================
%%  Car Rental Management System – State Diagram
%%  Entity: Contract / Rental Lifecycle
%% ============================================================
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CarBrowsing : Customer visits portal

    CarBrowsing --> CarSelected : Customer selects a car
    CarSelected --> DatesPicked : Customer picks rental dates
    DatesPicked --> PriceVerified : System calculates rental cost

    PriceVerified --> ContractDraft : Customer initiates booking
    ContractDraft --> PendingPayment : Customer confirms contract
    ContractDraft --> Abandoned : Customer cancels booking

    PendingPayment --> PaymentProcessing : Payment submitted
    PaymentProcessing --> PaymentFailed : Gateway rejection / error
    PaymentFailed --> PendingPayment : Customer retries
    PaymentFailed --> Abandoned : Customer gives up

    PaymentProcessing --> PaymentSuccessful : Transaction approved

    PaymentSuccessful --> ContractActive : Contract activated ✅
    ContractActive --> RentalInProgress : Pickup completed
    
    RentalInProgress --> ReturnScheduled : Return date approaching
    ReturnScheduled --> Completed : Vehicle returned
    Completed --> ReceiptGenerated : Confirmation generated
    ReceiptGenerated --> [*]

    ContractActive --> EarlyReturn : Customer returns car early
    EarlyReturn --> ReceiptGenerated

    RentalInProgress --> OverdueAlert : Return date passed
    OverdueAlert --> Overdue : Vehicle not returned
    Overdue --> ReceiptGenerated : Late fees calculated

    ContractActive --> CancellationRequested : Customer requests cancellation
    CancellationRequested --> CancellationApproved : Admin approves
    CancellationApproved --> Refund : Refund processed
    CancellationRequested --> CancellationRejected : Admin rejects
    CancellationRejected --> ContractActive

    Refund --> [*]
    Abandoned --> [*]
    CancellationRejected --> [*]

    note right of PaymentProcessing
        Calls external payment gateway.
        Timeout after 60 seconds.
    end note

    note right of ContractActive
        Car is now rented. Status updated to RENTED.
        Reminder emails sent to customer.
    end note

    note right of Overdue
        Late fees may apply based on
        rental agreement terms.
    end note
